      "writtenOn": "2016-11-08T22:15:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Hm, I\u0027m not sure I really see confusion arising with srgb. I\u0027m not opposed to \"_integer_\", but then what will we call unsigned integer formats, \"_unsigned_integer_\"?",
